WEBVTT

00:03:59.139 --> 00:04:03.269
With garlands, money, tilaks,
He is lost in pilgrimages

00:04:12.729 --> 00:04:16.969
Goes to villages, entertains the world
But has no concern for his own body

00:04:23.640 --> 00:04:28.959
When on the scale of discretion
people saw each other,

00:04:28.960 --> 00:04:34.319
they realized that on the basis of love
and compassion, they are the same.